    "body": "Example:\r\n```\r\npragma experimental SMTChecker;\r\n  \r\ncontract C {\r\n    uint[] a;\r\n    uint[][] b;\r\n    function f(uint x) public {\r\n        uint[] storage s = b[5];\r\n        a[0] = x;\r\n        s[1] = 2;\r\n        assert(a[0] == x);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nEven though `s` could be pointing to `a`, assigning `s[1]` shouldn't change `a[0]`.\r\nCurrently the assertion is reported as false, but it should be safe.",
